    "name": "PACS - Post Apocalypse Courier Service: Co-op Delivery Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3079190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你有本事把你的<strong>“末世快递服务”（Post Apocalypse Courier Service, PACS）</strong>从一个不起眼的小团队，发展成废土上最顶尖的快递公司吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏可供最多 4 名玩家联机合作递送包裹，体验刺激的在线合作玩法，在末世中赢得一席之地</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶载具穿越极端天气与险恶地形</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >徒步或驾车搜寻物资，维持生存并修理设备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用引擎、车轮、电池、传动系统、车身等部件自由定制你的载具！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打包包裹，管理库存，巧妙规划运输空间和材料</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请始终佩戴公司配发的防毒面具</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/fbbe31f566e5963959d4f9a43ca96e4d.poster.avif?t=1772206856\" width=780 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/fbbe31f566e5963959d4f9a43ca96e4d.webm?t=1772206856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/6b65497ece7605d3a528e9993d7aea65.avif?t=1772206856\" width=1560 height=310 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/64ac72526ba8273a918c6878a3e63e38.poster.avif?t=1772206856\" width=780 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/64ac72526ba8273a918c6878a3e63e38.webm?t=1772206856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（想在这个末世中生存下来，你需要路线和计划）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受人类最后据点的快递订单，改装你的载具，确保你和你的队员能基本不受辐射地抵达目的地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心打包！货物可能形状怪异、易爆，甚至具有放射性。我们可不想发生什么意外！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/fd91d2cfed46069dac9a5b959430d721.avif?t=1772206856\" width=1560 height=310 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/29ed5d0243163df90efe825cffa6a94b.poster.avif?t=1772206856\" width=780 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/29ed5d0243163df90efe825cffa6a94b.webm?t=1772206856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（达成在末世中准时送达包裹的奇迹）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >龟裂的路面和杂草丛生的小径，在你与满意顾客之间，构成了布满危险的地貌。在末世地形与恶劣天气中驾驶，同时确保包裹安全无损。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以与朋友结伴组成车队，也可以独自闯入未知——无论如何，送达、拿到报酬并活到明天才是关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/c3d508c1e2e30924a6696d84489bd6c8.avif?t=1772206856\" width=1560 height=310 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/0272c9f35f11ee3cf0bfbac8859e08ee.poster.avif?t=1772206856\" width=780 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079190/extras/0272c9f35f11ee3cf0bfbac8859e08ee.webm?t=1772206856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（快递员成长之路）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >徒步或驾车穿梭在残破的世界中，搜寻零件以升级载具，提升运载能力，并收集生存物资。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索新区域，扩展你的快递服务，迎接更多挑战——但别忘了偶尔放慢脚步，感受一下辐射的气息（警告：嗅闻行为必须通过公司配发的防毒面具进行）。如果在恰当的时机与朋友们共赏雾霾，末世的多样地形亦可显现出另类的美。</p>",
